// Leap Year Test in Dot dot

[2000, 2024, 1900, 2023] >> do each:
    @ >> year.
    (year % 400 == 0) || (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0) >> check:
        is true:
            "{0}年はうるう年です (1)" & year >> Format >> Display.
        else:
            "{0}年は平年です (0)" & year >> Format >> Display.
    ..
..
